description: A vulnerability was determined in itsourcecode E-Logbook with Health Monitoring System for COVID-19 1.0 on COVID. This affects an unknown function of the file /print_reports_prev.php. Executing manipulation of the argument profile_id can lead to cross site scripting. It is possible to launch the attack remotely. The exploit has been publicly disclosed and may be utilized.

product.name: E-Logbook with Health Monitoring System for COVID-19
